        <updateDate>2020-10-07T14:53:46Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Coronavirus Victims Compensation Fund Act of 2020</b></p> <p>This bill allows individuals to file claims and receive compensation for harm or death suffered as a result of COVID-19 (i.e., coronavirus disease 2019).</p> <p>A Special Master appointed by the Department of Justice must review claims submitted and determine if a claimant&nbsp;is eligible for compensation, the extent of the harm to the claimant, and the amount of compensation to be awarded.</p> </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
